    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions.",
